{"tid":459603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"失蹤5年女兒突然報夢稱被殺 家人終成功找出埋屍地點","createTime":"2017-11-06T01:45:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-06T02:24:11.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"be459a54c8793f5d4ede1026d259fca34612f94a","tid":459603,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T01:45:38.000Z","msg":"泰國一名女子聲稱失蹤5年的女兒突然向她報夢，說自己已被殺並點出埋屍地點，她隨即到警署報案。警方跟隨她去報稱的埋屍地調查，竟真的掘出一具屍骨，將作DNA檢驗確認其身份。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171105/large/1509860136_66db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171105%2Flarge%2F1509860136_66db.jpg&h=b85afc55&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n女子佔提拉憶述，2011年2月有朋友稱介紹她的16歲女兒到曼谷工作，朋友表示會好好照顧她並會每周送她回家一次，然而她自此就沒再見過女兒。<br />\n<br />\n佔提拉表示女兒最初用僱主的電話與她聯絡2次，最後一次是在2011年4月，當時女兒說想回家，但其後失蹤。佔提拉曾與朋友嘗試找她，一直無法尋回，即使報了警但案件一直沒有進展。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171105/large/1509860165_959a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171105%2Flarge%2F1509860165_959a.jpg&h=f46e10f1&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n至今年10月中旬，她收到消息指女兒被虐致死而且遭埋屍，其後又指女兒報夢告訴她埋屍之地，她於是到警局報警。她聲稱憑衣服和頭髮已認出屍骨的確屬於其女兒。當局會作DNA檢驗確認死者身份，暫時拘捕了3人調查。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171105/large/1509860134_4c1b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171105%2Flarge%2F1509860134_4c1b.jpg&h=e792b9ea&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171106/57419626\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171106%2F57419626&d=PvPIn4BCo7xNqJ%2FbUytAszCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=f4ca7088\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171106%2F57419626&h=09696d0b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171106/57419626</a>"},{"pid":"903575f108eb5a43f4977bb1c0d0f31b7be3ab2a","tid":459603,"uid":16061,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T01:46:41.000Z","msg":"自己埋完屍頂唔順個女每晚纏繞佢？"},{"pid":"cebc6640eacd4c63438b58fb42c4766db9f0f7c8","tid":459603,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T01:49:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己埋完屍頂唔順個女每晚纏繞佢？</blockquote><br />\n暫時拘捕了3人調查。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7868428921504c51c1edcaa4b02eb4fd28c5d4e9","tid":459603,"uid":72058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T02:17:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"460c90a2f87f49be207d41cdc7f50a29d63df664","tid":459603,"uid":123224,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T02:19:20.000Z","msg":"連登未成年探員全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b293086f72f5d1c46e9d0624c12a78bfb10b77d","tid":459603,"uid":4213,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T02:19:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n登乜柒場<br />\n估都估到係家人殺架啦<br />\n報你老母夢咩<br />\n庸人多自擾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"948bcefd10b75abdecf79ba6e2b261397ae30745","tid":459603,"uid":10442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T02:22:10.000Z","msg":"BORDER"},{"pid":"df7acde007aa4309e2a25f4bfeba833d8b8aff10","tid":459603,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T02:23:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkg